name: Belgian Air Force A321-231 [CS-TRJ] Taxi and Takeoff from Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
YYC was treated to a visit from the Belgian Air Force's A321 yesterday, along with a French Air Force A400M (which I sadly missed). Here they are leaving again today on board their A321 operated by HiFly, heading to Iqaluit and on to Bordeaux. ATC is included, and sorry for any blurriness.

Thanks for watching!
